1 TITL France, Military Conscripts of Seine
1 PUBL MyHeritage
1 TEXT <p>A period of 3 years' military service was obligatory for most young men as needed from 1889 to 1920. The required enlistment period was reduced to 12 months in 1920.</p>
2 CONC <p>These records are an excellent resource for tracing the lives of young men in France throughout conscription and provide a glimpse into the lives of soldiers into World War I.</p>
2 CONC <p>This collection was added following MyHeritage's acquisition of Filae.</p>
